prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor illustration for a greeting card front. The scene is set on a beautiful, whimsical tropical beach. In the center, a cartoon-style woman, representing Lao Lao, is lounging joyfully in an oversized, clear boba tea cup that has been repurposed as a hot tub, complete with tapioca pearls floating around her like bubbles. She is wearing a cute bathing suit and sunglasses, relaxing with a happy, laughing expression. The ocean waves gently lap at the shore, rendered in soft turquoise and cerulean watercolor washes. Palm trees with lush green fronds sway gently in the background. Instead of coconuts, the palm trees are humorously growing giant boba tea drinks, complete with colorful fat straws sticking out of the top. The sand is a warm, soft yellow, and the overall style is flat 2D with soft edges and a lighthearted, dreamy feel. In the center of the image, written in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text: "Happy Birthday, Lao Lao!"
